| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6337 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b54a8560-c003-5b9d-a279-0e607b2ef8c0"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
